# 5. 希望を届ける歌で

Rin: *Wince* That was way too bright...
Rin: Huh? This looks like...
???: Wow, look at how big this stage is...!
Rin: I saw lots of stages back there, but this one seems to be the biggest!
Rin: And this crowd's huge...! This is so cool...
Rin: They want to spread hope...
Rin: That's what the owners of the feeling which made this SEKAI feel...
Rin: Which means, I...
Rin: I also want to spread hope to everyone as an idol!
Rin: I know your wishes are going to come true!
Rin: Oh...!
Rin: Everyone! Let's have lots and lots of fun together today!
Rin: ーー♪ ーー♪
Rin: Yeah...
Rin: (Wanting to help them but not being able to was really frustrating...)
Rin: (But this me is doing everything she can for them in my place.)
Rin: You can do it, me!
Rin: ーー♪ ーー...♪
Rin: Thanks for listening, you guys!
???: Rin!
Rin: Oh...
Miku: There you are!
Rin: Hi, Miku!
Rin: This stage is so big and there was such a huge crowd here that I couldn't help but start singing♪
Miku: Oh, really?!
Miku: What a coincidence! I was actually just singing over on that stage♪
Rin: Hehe. I wish I could've seen your performance, Miku.
Rin: Still, it's amazing how there are all these stages here...
Rin: They must all represent how Haruka and the others feel.
Miku: *Nod* I hope we get to meet them soon♪
Miku: They must really love idols if their feelings were able to produce this SEKAI.
Miku: I have to also think that they're kind and wonderful people who are willing to give their all to bring others hope!
Rin: Definitely! I mean, it's so obvious from all these stages that they really want to spread hope to everyone!
Rin: Which means we also gotta do our best, Miku...!
Rin: We'll sing, dance, spread hope and help them discover their true feelings...
Rin: And someday, we're gonna perform on this stage with them!
Miku: Absolutely!
Rin: (They're both so cheerful and optimistic... I feel more hopeful after just listening to them.)
Rin: They may not be able to get their feelings across right away...
Rin: But I know the way you two perform is going to inspire so much hope in them.
Rin: So, do your best...!
Rin: Let's do this, Miku!
Miku: Okay! Let's make this the best show ever♪
Rin: W-Wait, does this mean I get to see them perform...?!
Rin: Hehe... Since I'm here, I might as well have some fun!
Miku: Here we go, everyone!
Rin: We're gonna have so much fun together♪
Rin: Wow! They're so cute!
Rin: Go, Miku! Go, me!
